15/04/2008
BRUSSELS, Belgium -- EU Enlargement Commissioner Olli Rehn met on Monday (April 14th) with Cypriot Foreign Minister Markos Kyprianou about new opportunities to resolve the long-standing division between Greek Cypriots and Turkish Cypriots. Rehn said he was encouraged by the strong commitment of the new Cypriot government to launch constructive talks under the auspices of the UN. The leaders of the two communities met recently about resuming reunification talks this summer. (ABHaber, CNA, Kuna - 14/04/08) 
